Welcome to contribute your effort.

## What can I do?

*   Join QQ group and forum to feedback on ZUI;
*   Go to [Open source China](http://git.oschina.net/wwccss/zui) or [Github](https://github.com/easysoft/zui) to **Star** or **Fork** this project;
*   Fork this project, better ZUI documents, optimize codes, or add new components to make ZUI better;
*   Follow ZUI plans and become a ZUI developer.

## What can I get？

Unfortunately, you are not getting any material rewards for contributing to ZUI.(Not excluded getting a small gift from [Nature Easy Soft](http://en.easysoft.ltd/).) However, I believe that you have gained:

*   Add useful components to ZUI, so it is easier to use it in your project;
*   Witness your work to help more people;
*   Your contribution to ZUI will be marked in the document;

If you have other issues to talk about, please contact[Nature Easy Soft](http://www.easysoft.ltd/), or send an email to sunhao@cnezsoft.com.
